<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>New Volunteer Application</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background: #FFF0EA; color: #373735; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; }
    .header { border-bottom: 2px solid #FAD062; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .brand { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #015243; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .tagline { font-size: 11px; color: #7a756f; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 4px; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #015243; margin: 0 0 8px; line-height: 1.2; }
    p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #373735; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .row { background: #f7e6dd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; margin: 12px 0; }
    .label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #7a756f; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; }
    .value { font-size: 14px; color: #373735; margin-top: 3px; white-space: pre-wrap; }
    .footer { margin-top: 36px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #e6d4c8; font-size: 11px; color: #7a756f; }
    a { color: #015243; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="brand">Badlaav</div>
      <div class="tagline">Volunteer application</div>
    </div>

    <h1>New volunteer application</h1>
    <p>Someone has applied to volunteer. Review and respond from the admin panel.</p>

    <div class="row"><div class="label">Name</div><div class="value">{{name}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Email</div><div class="value">{{email}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Phone</div><div class="value">{{phone}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">City</div><div class="value">{{city}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Batch attended / interested in</div><div class="value">{{batchAttended}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Skills</div><div class="value">{{skills}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Availability</div><div class="value">{{availability}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Can travel</div><div class="value">{{canTravel}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Why volunteer</div><div class="value">{{whyVolunteer}}</div></div>
    <div class="row"><div class="label">Message to Arjun</div><div class="value">{{messageToArjun}}</div></div>

    <div class="footer">
      Badlaav · Ambajogai, Maharashtra<br />
      <a href="mailto:iambadlaav@gmail.com">iambadlaav@gmail.com</a> · 7409339740
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
